Timeline Figure Example

Chuck Cleland

June 25, 2021 09:11:25 AM EDT

library(data.table)
library(tidyverse)
DT <- expand.grid(Task = c('Hiring and training',
                           'Finalize protocols, surveys',
                           'Create administrative data cohort',
                           'Recruitment',
                           'Intervention',
                           'NNAL and EMA measurement',
                           'Study visits  BL, 8-, 26, 52-weeks',
                           'Carbon monoxide and urine toxicology',
                           'Data cleaning',
                           'Data analysis',
                           'Manuscript preparation'),
                  Smonth = 1:60)

setDT(DT)

DT[, Year := car::recode(Smonth, "1:12='Year 1';
                                 13:24='Year 2';
                                 25:36='Year 3';
                                 37:48='Year 4';
                                 49:60='Year 5'", as.factor = TRUE)]

DT[, Month := rep(rep(1:12, each = 11), 5)]

DT[, Task := ordered(Task, levels = rev(c('Hiring and training','Finalize protocols, surveys',
                                          'Create administrative data cohort',
                           'Recruitment','Intervention','NNAL and EMA measurement',
                           'Study visits  BL, 8-, 26, 52-weeks',
                           'Carbon monoxide and urine toxicology',
                           'Data cleaning','Data analysis','Manuscript preparation')))]
DT[, Active := 0]
DT[Task == 'Hiring and training' & Smonth %in% 1:7, Active := 1]
DT[Task == 'Finalize protocols, surveys' & Smonth %in% 1:8, Active := 1]
DT[Task == 'Create administrative data cohort' & Smonth %in% 9:21, Active := 1]
DT[Task == 'Recruitment' & Smonth %in% 13:38, Active := 1]
DT[Task == 'Intervention' & Smonth %in% 16:40, Active := 1]
DT[Task == 'NNAL and EMA measurement' & Smonth %in% 16:40, Active := 1]
DT[Task == 'Study visits  BL, 8-, 26, 52-weeks' & Smonth %in% 16:52, Active := 1]
DT[Task == 'Carbon monoxide and urine toxicology' & Smonth %in% 16:52, Active := 1]
DT[Task == 'Data cleaning' & Smonth %in% 22:52, Active := 1]
DT[Task == 'Data analysis' & Smonth %in% 25:56, Active := 1]
DT[Task == 'Manuscript preparation' & Smonth %in% c(9:12,25:60), Active := 1]
tfig <- ggplot(DT, aes(y = Task, x = Month, color = factor(Active), fill = factor(Active))) + 
  geom_point(pch = 22, size = 2) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("white","black")) +
  scale_color_manual(values = c("lightgrey","black")) +
  facet_wrap(~ Year, nrow = 1) +
  labs(x = "", y = "") +
  theme_minimal() +
  theme(legend.position = "none",
        axis.text.x = element_blank(), 
        axis.text.y = element_text(color = "black", size = 9, face = "bold"),
        strip.text.x = element_text(size = 12, face = "bold"),
        panel.grid.major = element_blank(), 
        panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
        plot.margin = margin(0, 0, -4, 0, "pt"))
print(tfig)

Create a PNG Image File for MS-Word

ggsave(filename = "Timeline-Figure-Example.png", 
       plot = tfig, width = 8, height = 2, units = "in", dpi = 600)
